      <title>Apollo，KKR将在竞标Caixabank贷款的下一个回合</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/apollo-kkr-to-move-to-next-round-in-bidding-for-caixabank-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Caixabank SA选择了Apollo Global Management Inc.，KKR＆amp;据熟悉此事的人们称，Co Inc.和Balbec Capital Management LP竞标了价值约6亿欧元（6.5亿美元）的不表现抵押贷款的投资组合。]]></description>
