    <item>
      <title>新兴市场股票随着美国关税的担忧而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/emerging-currencies-steady-after-china-data-with-us-tariffs-eyed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者急切地离开唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的全球关税计划，新兴市场的股票连续第三天暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-31/emerging-currencies-steady-after-china-data-with-us-tariffs-eyed</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 31 Mar 2025 04:03:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>S＆amp; p 500装饰掉落，因为关税摇摆不定地球：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/us-stock-futures-tumble-ahead-of-new-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统的关税推广前几天，一阵新的波动率袭击了全球市场，对经济放缓驱动股票的担忧加剧了，因为交易者急于兑现债券和黄金的安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-30/us-stock-futures-tumble-ahead-of-new-trump-tariffs-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 30 Mar 2025 22:31:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
